data.name: txtContent3.Text
data.value: If the bank does not receive any response from you to reactivate your account within sixty (60) days from the date stipulated in this letter , your account will be treated as dormant account subjected to the application of law as provided by the Bangko Sentral ng Pilipinas.

data.name: txtContent1.Text
data.value: Thank you for banking with Katipunan Bank, Inc. and we hope to continuously serve your financial needs. Your ongoing business with the institution is very important to us, therefore we must call your attention to a matter regarding your account.
